[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 01:16, 5 July 2025 (UTC)}} This is a '''List of Shikinaisha in Buzen Province''' or the list of shrines in [[Buzen Province]] which is present in the {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|ja|延喜式神名帳|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engishiki Jinmyōchō|13=User:Immanuelle/Engishiki Jinmyōchō|qq=}}
